dct_title_s: Shell Reisekarte : Jugoslawien, Griechenland / Mairs Geographischer Verlag.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Map shows road and transportation networks, sea routes, distances, places of interest to tourists, borders, capitals. Purple stamp on recto: Army Map Service Library, 24 August 1965, accession number 8519. Recto shows city plans of Akropolis, Delphi, Epidauros, and Olympia (no scales).
